spec_data.Description:
Cwd::Guard can change the current directory (chdir) using a limited scope.

  use Cwd::Guard qw/cwd_guard/;
  use Cwd;

  my $dir = getcwd;
  MYBLOCK: {
    my $guard = cwd_guard('/tmp/xxxxx') or die
      "failed chdir: $Cwd::Guard::Error";
    ... # chdir to /tmp/xxxxx
  }
  ... # back to $dir
